annotationA: Double hit (Dhit) negatively regulates Galpha signaling and is involved in several GPCR-mediated signaling and developmental programs, such as asymmetric cell division in the sensory organ lineage
annotationB: Regulator of G-protein signalling 7, isoform A; GTPase activator activity; signal transducer activity.
